Draghi Spokesperson Says He Never Commented on EFSF License

-- B y   G a b i   T h e s i n g
-- 
2011-10-03T13:43:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/draghi-spokesperson-says-he-never-commented-on-efsf-license.html
A spokesperson for incoming European
Central Bank President  Mario Draghi  rejected a Der Spiegel
article saying he didn’t oppose granting a banking licence to
 Europe ’s temporary rescue fund.  The spokesperson said the Spiegel report is not accurate as
Draghi had never commented on the matter. The Spiegel report
cite anyone. The spokesperson declined to be identified in line 
with Bank of  Italy  ground rules.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Gabi Thesing in London at 
 gthesing@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
